meaningMnemonic: I'm going to <kanji>cut off</kanji> the part of me that I'm trying to <kanji>diagnose</kanji>... well, not literally cut off, but cut off my diagnosing. I have come to a conclusion. A <vocabulary>diagnosis</vocabulary>!
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
